---
import ChapterLayout from '../layouts/ChapterLayout.astro';
---

<ChapterLayout 
  title="My Tech Journey - Chapter II" 
  description="Follow my path from curiosity to expertise, with all the learning moments in between"
  chapter="Chapter II" 
  chapterTitle="My Tech Journey" 
  chapterColor="sky"
>
  <!-- Main Content -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6">
      <!-- Introduction -->
      <div class="text-center mb-20">
        <h2 class="font-heading text-3xl lg:text-4xl font-semibold text-ink-800 mb-6">
          From Curiosity to Code
        </h2>
        <p class="text-lg text-ink-700 max-w-3xl mx-auto leading-relaxed">
          Every developer has a unique story of how they fell in love with code. Mine began with a simple question: 
          "How do computers actually work?" This curiosity led me down a rabbit hole that I'm still exploring today.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Timeline -->
      <div class="relative">
        <!-- Timeline Line -->
        <div class="absolute left-4 lg:left-1/2 top-0 bottom-0 w-1 bg-gradient-to-b from-sky-200 via-mint-200 to-blush-200 rounded-full transform lg:-translate-x-1/2"></div>

        <!-- Timeline Items -->
        <div class="space-y-12">
          <!-- Item 1: The Beginning -->
          <div class="relative flex items-center">
            <div class="lg:w-1/2 lg:pr-8 lg:text-right">
              <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-white to-sky-50 rounded-2xl p-6 shadow-soft border-l-4 border-sky-400 ml-12 lg:ml-0">
                <div class="flex items-center mb-4 lg:justify-end">
                  <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-gradient-to-br from-sky-200 to-sky-400 flex items-center justify-center">
                    <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-white" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                      <path d="M12,2L13.09,8.26L22,9L13.09,9.74L12,16L10.91,9.74L2,9L10.91,8.26L12,2Z"/>
                    </svg>
                  </div>
                  <span class="text-sky-600 font-medium ml-3 lg:mr-3 lg:ml-0">2019</span>
                </div>
                <h3 class="font-heading text-xl font-semibold text-ink-800 mb-3">The Spark</h3>
                <p class="text-ink-700 text-sm">
                  It all started with a broken computer and too much curiosity. Instead of taking it to a repair shop, 
                  I spent hours watching YouTube videos learning how to fix it myself. That's when I realized technology 
                  wasn't magic – it was logical, beautiful, and learnable.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
            
            <!-- Timeline Dot -->
            <div class="absolute left-4 lg:left-1/2 w-8 h-8 bg-gradient-to-br from-sky-400 to-sky-600 rounded-full transform lg:-translate-x-1/2 flex items-center justify-center">
              <div class="w-3 h-3 bg-white rounded-full"></div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="lg:w-1/2 lg:pl-8 hidden lg:block"></div>
          </div>

          <!-- Item 2: First Code -->
          <div class="relative flex items-center">
            <div class="lg:w-1/2 lg:pr-8 hidden lg:block"></div>
            
            <div class="absolute left-4 lg:left-1/2 w-8 h-8 bg-gradient-to-br from-mint-400 to-mint-600 rounded-full transform lg:-translate-x-1/2 flex items-center justify-center">
              <div class="w-3 h-3 bg-white rounded-full"></div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="lg:w-1/2 lg:pl-8">
              <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-white to-mint-50 rounded-2xl p-6 shadow-soft border-l-4 border-mint-400 ml-12 lg:ml-0">
                <div class="flex items-center mb-4">
                  <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-gradient-to-br from-mint-200 to-mint-400 flex items-center justify-center">
                    <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-white" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                      <path d="M8,3A2,2 0 0,0 6,5V9A2,2 0 0,1 4,11H3V13H4A2,2 0 0,1 6,15V19A2,2 0 0,0 8,21H10V19H8V14A2,2 0 0,0 6,12A2,2 0 0,0 8,10V5H10V3M16,3A2,2 0 0,1 18,5V9A2,2 0 0,0 20,11H21V13H20A2,2 0 0,0 18,15V19A2,2 0 0,1 16,21H14V19H16V14A2,2 0 0,1 18,12A2,2 0 0,1 16,10V5H14V3"/>
                    </svg>
                  </div>
                  <span class="text-mint-600 font-medium ml-3">2020</span>
                </div>
                <h3 class="font-heading text-xl font-semibold text-ink-800 mb-3">Hello, World!</h3>
                <p class="text-ink-700 text-sm">
                  My first line of code was the classic "Hello, World!" in Python. I still remember the rush of excitement 
                  when those two words appeared on my screen. It was like discovering a new language that could bring 
                  ideas to life through logic and creativity.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Item 3: Deep Dive -->
          <div class="relative flex items-center">
            <div class="lg:w-1/2 lg:pr-8 lg:text-right">
              <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-white to-lavender-50 rounded-2xl p-6 shadow-soft border-l-4 border-lavender-400 ml-12 lg:ml-0">
                <div class="flex items-center mb-4 lg:justify-end">
                  <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-gradient-to-br from-lavender-200 to-lavender-400 flex items-center justify-center">
                    <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-white" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                      <path d="M12,2A10,10 0 0,0 2,12A10,10 0 0,0 12,22A10,10 0 0,0 22,12A10,10 0 0,0 12,2M12,4A8,8 0 0,1 20,12A8,8 0 0,1 12,20A8,8 0 0,1 4,12A8,8 0 0,1 12,4M12,6A6,6 0 0,0 6,12A6,6 0 0,0 12,18A6,6 0 0,0 18,12A6,6 0 0,0 12,6M12,8A4,4 0 0,1 16,12A4,4 0 0,1 12,16A4,4 0 0,1 8,12A4,4 0 0,1 12,8Z"/>
                    </svg>
                  </div>
                  <span class="text-lavender-600 font-medium ml-3 lg:mr-3 lg:ml-0">2021</span>
                </div>
                <h3 class="font-heading text-xl font-semibold text-ink-800 mb-3">The Deep Dive</h3>
                <p class="text-ink-700 text-sm">
                  I decided to take programming seriously and enrolled in computer science courses. Data structures, 
                  algorithms, and object-oriented programming became my new obsessions. Every concept was a puzzle 
                  waiting to be solved.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="absolute left-4 lg:left-1/2 w-8 h-8 bg-gradient-to-br from-lavender-400 to-lavender-600 rounded-full transform lg:-translate-x-1/2 flex items-center justify-center">
              <div class="w-3 h-3 bg-white rounded-full"></div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="lg:w-1/2 lg:pl-8 hidden lg:block"></div>
          </div>

          <!-- Item 4: First Project -->
          <div class="relative flex items-center">
            <div class="lg:w-1/2 lg:pr-8 hidden lg:block"></div>
            
            <div class="absolute left-4 lg:left-1/2 w-8 h-8 bg-gradient-to-br from-butter-400 to-butter-600 rounded-full transform lg:-translate-x-1/2 flex items-center justify-center">
              <div class="w-3 h-3 bg-white rounded-full"></div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="lg:w-1/2 lg:pl-8">
              <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-white to-butter-50 rounded-2xl p-6 shadow-soft border-l-4 border-butter-400 ml-12 lg:ml-0">
                <div class="flex items-center mb-4">
                  <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-gradient-to-br from-butter-200 to-butter-400 flex items-center justify-center">
                    <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-white" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                      <path d="M13,9H18.5L13,3.5V9M6,2H14L20,8V20A2,2 0 0,1 18,22H6C4.89,22 4,21.1 4,20V4C4,2.89 4.89,2 6,2M15,18V16H6V18H15M18,14V12H6V14H18Z"/>
                    </svg>
                  </div>
                  <span class="text-butter-600 font-medium ml-3">2022</span>
                </div>
                <h3 class="font-heading text-xl font-semibold text-ink-800 mb-3">First Real Project</h3>
                <p class="text-ink-700 text-sm">
                  Built my first web application - a simple task manager. It wasn't pretty, but it worked! This project 
                  taught me about databases, user interfaces, and the satisfaction of creating something others could 
                  actually use.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Item 5: Advanced Learning -->
          <div class="relative flex items-center">
            <div class="lg:w-1/2 lg:pr-8 lg:text-right">
              <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-white to-blush-50 rounded-2xl p-6 shadow-soft border-l-4 border-blush-400 ml-12 lg:ml-0">
                <div class="flex items-center mb-4 lg:justify-end">
                  <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-gradient-to-br from-blush-200 to-blush-400 flex items-center justify-center">
                    <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-white" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                      <path d="M5,3H7V5H5V10A2,2 0 0,1 3,8V5A2,2 0 0,1 5,3M19,3A2,2 0 0,1 21,5V8A2,2 0 0,1 19,10V5H17V3H19M3,13A2,2 0 0,1 5,11V16H7V18H5A2,2 0 0,1 3,16V13M21,13V16A2,2 0 0,1 19,18H17V16H19V11A2,2 0 0,1 21,13Z"/>
                    </svg>
                  </div>
                  <span class="text-blush-600 font-medium ml-3 lg:mr-3 lg:ml-0">2023</span>
                </div>
                <h3 class="font-heading text-xl font-semibold text-ink-800 mb-3">Machine Learning & AI</h3>
                <p class="text-ink-700 text-sm">
                  Discovered the fascinating world of artificial intelligence and machine learning. Started with simple 
                  linear regression and worked my way up to neural networks. The possibility of making computers 
                  "think" was mind-blowing.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="absolute left-4 lg:left-1/2 w-8 h-8 bg-gradient-to-br from-blush-400 to-blush-600 rounded-full transform lg:-translate-x-1/2 flex items-center justify-center">
              <div class="w-3 h-3 bg-white rounded-full"></div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="lg:w-1/2 lg:pl-8 hidden lg:block"></div>
          </div>

          <!-- Item 6: Present -->
          <div class="relative flex items-center">
            <div class="lg:w-1/2 lg:pr-8 hidden lg:block"></div>
            
            <div class="absolute left-4 lg:left-1/2 w-8 h-8 bg-gradient-to-br from-sky-400 to-mint-400 rounded-full transform lg:-translate-x-1/2 flex items-center justify-center">
              <div class="w-3 h-3 bg-white rounded-full"></div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="lg:w-1/2 lg:pl-8">
              <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-white to-sky-50 rounded-2xl p-6 shadow-soft border-l-4 border-sky-400 ml-12 lg:ml-0">
                <div class="flex items-center mb-4">
                  <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-gradient-to-br from-sky-200 to-mint-200 flex items-center justify-center">
                    <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-white" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                      <path d="M12,2A10,10 0 0,0 2,12A10,10 0 0,0 12,22A10,10 0 0,0 22,12A10,10 0 0,0 12,2M16.2,16.2L11,13V7H12.5V12.2L17,15.4L16.2,16.2Z"/>
                    </svg>
                  </div>
                  <span class="text-sky-600 font-medium ml-3">2024</span>
                </div>
                <h3 class="font-heading text-xl font-semibold text-ink-800 mb-3">The Journey Continues</h3>
                <p class="text-ink-700 text-sm">
                  Today, I'm working on my final year project, exploring cloud technologies, and contributing to 
                  open-source projects. Every day brings new challenges and opportunities to grow. The best part? 
                  I'm still as excited about coding as I was on day one.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Key Learnings -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-gradient-to-br from-sky-50 to-mint-50">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6">
      <div class="text-center mb-16">
        <h2 class="font-heading text-3xl lg:text-4xl font-semibold text-ink-800 mb-6">
          Key Learnings Along the Way
        </h2>
        <p class="text-ink-700 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
          Every milestone taught me something valuable. Here are the most important lessons that shaped my approach to development.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
        <!-- Learning 1 -->
        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 shadow-soft">
          <div class="w-16 h-16 rounded-full bg-gradient-to-br from-sky-300 to-sky-500 flex items-center justify-center mb-6 mx-auto">
            <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-white" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path d="M12,2C13.1,2 14,2.9 14,4C14,5.1 13.1,6 12,6C10.9,6 10,5.1 10,4C10,2.9 10.9,2 12,2M21,9V7L15,1H5C3.9,1 3,1.9 3,3V19C3,20.1 3.9,21 5,21H19C20.1,21 21,20.1 21,19V9M19,19H5V3H13V9H19V19Z"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-heading text-xl font-semibold text-ink-800 mb-4 text-center">Code is Communication</h3>
          <p class="text-ink-700 text-center">
            The best code isn't just functional—it tells a story. Writing clean, readable code isn't about showing off; 
            it's about being kind to your future self and your teammates.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Learning 2 -->
        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 shadow-soft">
          <div class="w-16 h-16 rounded-full bg-gradient-to-br from-mint-300 to-mint-500 flex items-center justify-center mb-6 mx-auto">
            <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-white" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path d="M15,9H9V5H15M12,19.2L18,14.2V9L12,4L6,9V14.2L12,19.2M12,2L20,8V16L12,22L4,16V8L12,2Z"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-heading text-xl font-semibold text-ink-800 mb-4 text-center">Embrace the Struggle</h3>
          <p class="text-ink-700 text-center">
            Those moments when you're stuck debugging for hours? They're not failures—they're growth opportunities. 
            Every error message is a teacher in disguise.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Learning 3 -->
        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 shadow-soft">
          <div class="w-16 h-16 rounded-full bg-gradient-to-br from-lavender-300 to-lavender-500 flex items-center justify-center mb-6 mx-auto">
            <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-white" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path d="M12,2A10,10 0 0,0 2,12A10,10 0 0,0 12,22A10,10 0 0,0 22,12A10,10 0 0,0 12,2Z"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-heading text-xl font-semibold text-ink-800 mb-4 text-center">Community Matters</h3>
          <p class="text-ink-700 text-center">
            Programming might seem solitary, but it's actually deeply collaborative. The developer community is 
            incredibly generous with knowledge, and giving back feels amazing.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Learning 4 -->
        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 shadow-soft">
          <div class="w-16 h-16 rounded-full bg-gradient-to-br from-butter-300 to-butter-500 flex items-center justify-center mb-6 mx-auto">
            <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-white" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path d="M2,21L23,12L2,3V10L17,12L2,14V21Z"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-heading text-xl font-semibold text-ink-800 mb-4 text-center">Technology Serves People</h3>
          <p class="text-ink-700 text-center">
            The coolest algorithm means nothing if it doesn't solve a real problem. Always ask: "How does this 
            make someone's life better?"
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Call to Action -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-gradient-to-r from-sky-100 to-mint-100">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 text-center">
      <h2 class="font-heading text-3xl font-semibold text-ink-800 mb-6">
        Next: The Tools That Power My Journey
      </h2>
      <p class="text-ink-700 mb-8 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
        Now that you've seen my path, let's explore the technologies, frameworks, and tools that help me bring ideas to life every day.
      </p>
      <a href="/toolkit" class="inline-flex items-center px-8 py-4 rounded-full bg-gradient-to-r from-sky-500 to-mint-500 text-white font-medium hover:shadow-chapter transition-all duration-300 hover:scale-105">
        <span>Read Chapter III: My Toolkit</span>
        <svg class="w-5 h-5 ml-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
          <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 7l5 5m0 0l-5 5m5-5H6"></path>
        </svg>
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>
</ChapterLayout> 